G </td><td class=\"left\">Togo </td><td class=\"left\">Togo </td><td class=\"left\">N </td></tr><tr><td class=\"left\">Tonga </td><td class=\"left\">TGA </td><td class=\"left\">TO </td><td class=\"left\">Tonga </td><td class=\"left\">Tonga </td><td class=\"left\">N </td></tr><tr><td class=\"left\">Trinidad and Tobago </td><td class=\"left\">TRI </td><td class=\"left\">TT </td><td class=\"left\">Trinidad & Tobago </td><td class=\"left\">Trinidad and Tobago </td><td class=\"left\">N </td></tr><tr><td class=\"left\">Tunisia </td><td class=\"left\">TUN </td><td class=\"left\">TN </td><td class=\"left\">Tunisia </td><td class=\"left\">Tunisia </td><td class=\"left\">N </td></tr><tr><td class=\"left\">Turkey </td><td class=\"left\">TUR </td><td class=\"left\">TR </td><td class=\"left\">Turkey </td><td class=\"left\">Turkey </td><td class=\"left\">N </td></tr><tr><td class=\"left\">Turkmenistan </td><td class=\"left\">TKM </td><td class=\"left\">TM </td><td class=\"left\">Turkmenistan </td><td class=\"left\">Turkmenistan </td><td class=\"left\">N </td></tr><tr><td class=\"left\">Uganda </td><td class=\"left\">UGA </td><td class=\"left\">UG </td><td class=\"left\">Uganda </td><td class=\"left\">Uganda </td><td class=\"left\">N </td></tr><tr><td class=\"left\">Ukraine </td><td class=\"left\">UKR </td><td class=\"left\">UA </td><td class=\"left\">Ukraine </td><td class=\"left\">Ukraine </td><td class=\"left\">N </td></tr><tr><td class=\"left\">United Arab Emirates </td><td class=\"left\">UAE </td><td class=\"left\">AE </td><td class=\"left\">United Arab Emirates </td><td class=\"left\">United Arab Emirates </td><td class=\"left\">N </td></tr><tr><td class=\"bold left\">United Kingdom </td><td class=\"bold left\">GBR </td><td class=\"bold left\">GB </td><td class=\"bold left\">Great Britain </td><td class=\"bold left\">UK </td><td class=\"bold left\">Y </td></tr><tr><td class=\"bold left\">United States </td><td class=\"bold left\">USA </td><td class=\"bold left\">US </td><td 